{"tid":699264,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(乒壇) 點睇日本神童 張本智和 輾壓中國乒乓?","createTime":"2018-06-12T11:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T13:06:24.000Z","uid":104658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f8571a81215aec85e756eade5203504808c4e66e","tid":699264,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:24:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180610/s00006/1528622921879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180610%2Fs00006%2F1528622921879&d=3k50zcR32xsrFzfRN4TQXjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ce0fcb77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180610%2Fs00006%2F1528622921879&h=39c67366\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180610/s00006/1528622921879</a><br />\n<br />\n14歲日本球手張本智和在日本乒乓球公開賽決賽擊敗中國的張繼科，繼去年的捷克公開賽後再奪成人賽冠軍。另一日本球手伊藤美誠較早前亦為東道主贏得女單冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n張繼科今早4強因德國名將波爾因傷退賽而自動晉級，首兩局險勝張本智和11：8及11：9。但在8強曾挫前世界第一的國手馬龍，月尾才滿15歲的張本智和隨後兩局以11：9、11：4追平局數。兩人再各贏一局下戰至決勝局「刁時」，最終張本智和13：11搶走最後一局，繼上星期中國公開賽外圍賽後再贏張繼科，在主場揚威，並會成為日本一哥。張本去年在捷克未對上過中國球手，今次比賽更見其能耐。<br />\n<br />\n伊藤美誠在女單以局數4：2擊敗中國小將王曼昱，令日本包辦兩項單打金牌。加上韓國組合贏出男雙，中國只能在女雙及昨日的混雙收穫冠軍。"},{"pid":"cb66aef4174058ae37dab0cb790bdda7c6cbf0f4","tid":699264,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XLO3B8nQnSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXLO3B8nQnSA&d=3k50zcR32xsrFzfRN4TQXjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=fbeee576\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XLO3B8nQnSA</a>"},{"pid":"bca61642130df6bad27ac535c66340b7187c6c01","tid":699264,"uid":104658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"2003年6月27日，生於日本仙台市，日本男子桌球選手，以13歲之齡殺入2017年世界錦標賽八強成名。<br />\n<br />\n在2017年世錦賽64強4-1擊敗日本頭號男單水谷隼，震驚整個桌球界。同年世界巡迴賽系列捷克公開賽張本橫掃歐美球手奪冠，成為最年輕巡迴賽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n2018年全日本桌球錦標賽決賽擊敗水谷隼，以14歲6個月之齡奪冠，打破水谷隼在2007年以17歲7個月締造的最年輕冠軍紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n主教練是父親張宇，前中國四川省隊。母親張凌亦來自四川，中國國乒一隊，曾出戰1995年世桌賽女單。張本智和與父親和妹妹在2014年歸化日本籍，改姓張本。"},{"pid":"69accd613172ad21b0d105d5904a08515c3bf1bb","tid":699264,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"宜加先得15歲 前途無可限量  應該未來十年都係佢玩曬<br />\n<br />\n好想睇佢同許昕直板砌返轉"},{"pid":"79534b256f21006e3e6058a8b40049b8644ba562","tid":699264,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"中国移民嚟"},{"pid":"3bce740cf9f6bffced51900b4792a42bff53931d","tid":699264,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"傷害支那人民感情"},{"pid":"656b905a6afb5fcb97c3fe19511713a0d47ffd01","tid":699264,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"中國人後代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7b87e71bb62a86f5350fa94a5aaf8fe9c6d2a5","tid":699264,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"15歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為純種日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c61ec7cf239da4957fd2cf4deff733ca9c5df7","tid":699264,"uid":39013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"79534b256f21006e3e6058a8b40049b8644ba562","tid":699264,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"中国移民嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:31:27.000Z","msg":"以夷制夷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha